  "body": "I've got the syncing issue before, `Syncing: state healing in progress`, and I fixed this by `geth removedb` and restart from scratch, and it works well.\r\nI run geth in docker. The problem is, after I stop the container and rerun the container with the volume of the datadir, I got the syncing issue again `Syncing: state healing in progress`.\r\nShould I kill the process elegently? And how?",
