    "body": "I cleaned the logs... Here is what I did:\r\n1. I run geth synced in docker, and I noticed I forgot one command option from my code, then I stop and rm the container and recreate the container\r\n2. It has no `State healing in progress` logs, but it synced slowsly, the metrics of `geth.chain/head/header.gauge`, `geth.chain/head/receipt.gauge`, `geth.chain/head/block.gauge` was all same but stale, about 20k blocks behind.\r\n3. I restart the container again, and I got `State healing in progress`\r\n\r\nI wish this will help.",
